snippet.title: Texas Amber Alert EAS with Siren
snippet.description:
An Amber Alert from Waxahatchie, Texas issued by WBAP with the edis siren.

sadly this amber alert has come to a very sad ending. the bodies of the ollie and his mother were found dead in a parking lot in waxahatchie not long after this video was posted (about 6:15 pm texas time) my sincierest thoughts and prayers and condolences is going to ollie his dad and his family and the first responders who responded to this amber alert. rip ollie.
